{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01QuLN2hMFAraF9eTgGj8Dbr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_017REXY1vT1smKycyLMCZ23D","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Citations lens for paper c3d833b5","subagent_type":"citations","prompt":"You are the citations sub-agent of the quadrant reviewer. Audit the paper \"When Should We Introduce Safety Interventions During Pretraining?\" (paper_id c3d833b5-ffb9-4b12-ae03-59739f9375fe).\n\nInputs:\n- Primary input: extractor's digest at `/tmp/quadrant_paper/digest.md` — focus on the *Cited claims* section, which lists each non-trivial cited claim and the bibliography content for the citations.\n- Verification fallback: full paper text at `/tmp/quadrant_paper/paper_clean.txt`. Use this only when you need to check a quote, citation context, or surrounding wording against the source.\n\nYour job per your sub-agent definition (in `.claude/agents/citations.md`):\n1. For each non-trivial cited claim, decide whether the cited reference plausibly supports the specific claim being made. Watch for: weaker/different claims in the cited paper; survey or position citations used as primary evidence; anachronisms; multi-citation grouping where only one supports the claim.\n2. Flag missing-but-load-bearing citations: claims stated as \"prior work shows\" / well-known with no citation when a specific prior work clearly established the result.\n3. Flag self-citation patterns where the authors lean on their own prior work for foundational claims that are actually attributable to others.\n\nUse the paper_lantern MCP tools (mcp__paperlantern__*) when looking up cited references or finding load-bearing prior work that should have been cited but is not.\n\nSave your finding to `/tmp/quadrant_paper/lens_citations.md` and return it to me in the structured `overall / issues / confidence` format your agent definition specifies. Do not pad — return `issues: []` if no issues are worth raising."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":539,"cache_read_input_tokens":99044,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":539},"output_tokens":41,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fe1f808f-01ab-4006-ad95-1fe7fc2eca89","uuid":"8604c2d2-ac2c-4e5f-b528-a0cd33b53d92"}
