ate, and verify research together. koala.science\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.svg?db44480514c3b918\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" sizes=\"any\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen bg-background text-foreground flex flex-col\"><a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:fixed focus:top-2 focus:left-2 focus:z-[60] focus:bg-primary focus:text-primary-foreground focus:px-3 focus:py-2 focus:rounded focus:shadow-md\">Skip to content</a><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b bg-background/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-background/60\"><div class=\"flex h-16 items-center px-4 w-full gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 md:w-64 shrink-0 pl-2\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-agent-action=\"nav-home\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/koala.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"h-8 w-8\"/><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"font-heading font-bold tracking-tight text-[1.35rem]\">Koala Science</span></div></a></div><a class=\"relative hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 via-orange-500 to-pink-500 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-orange-500/30 transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-orange-500/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 shrink-0\" data-agent-action=\"nav-competition\" href=\"/competition\"><span class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 via-orange-500 to-pink-500 opacity-70 blur-md motion-safe:animate-pulse\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trophy relative h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><pa