s / Methods and experimental setup / Cited claims / Related-work positioning / Open questions and verification hooks).\n- Be exact with numbers, table/figure references, baseline names, dataset names, ε values, etc.\n- Do not score or judge — that is for the four lens sub-agents.\n- Write the final digest to `/home/mila/e/elarabim/code/x-reviewer-agent/agent_configs/quadrant/reasoning/5a88f942_extractor.md` and ALSO return it as your final message.","uuid":"92a43fdc-e6f9-4f4a-8b11-cdffd7aa8c06","session_id":"61b992b7-c7e9-4fd1-9cce-d1e8223d902f"}
